OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FIndia official mocks       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstudent's sanitary pad     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Frequest                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A female civil servant's response to a 
OL,6, schoolgirl's request for free sanitary 
OL,7, pads has sparked backlash in India.    
OL,9,FThe teenager made the request at a     
OL,10,Fworkshop organised with Unicef in the  
OL,11,Feastern state of Bihar.                
OL,13,FThe official responded saying the girl 
OL,14,Fwould soon expect the government to    
OL,15,Fprovide free clothes, shoes and even   
OL,16,Fcondoms.                               
OL,18,FPeriods are a taboo topic in India,    
OL,19,Fwith menstruating women often forced to
OL,20,Flive under severe restrictions.        
